cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.NE, cs.CL

The paper is primarily focused on Machine Learning (ML) and its implementation in the browser, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses distributed computing, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The use of ML in mobile and field applications could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper briefly mentions privacy preserving computing, which could fall under cs.CL (Computation and Language).
